<D>__{the elevator wasn't working?}
<C>__{helena}
<D>__{no, it has a mind of its own.}
<A>__{a clock strikes four somewhere. and berlin knows he's lost it.}
<C>__{berlin}
<D>__{can i see your hands?}
<C>__{helena}
<D>__{my hands?}
<A>__{he takes her hands and helena immediately looks uncomfortable. he examines scars and she stares at him with her useless eyes.}
