<D>__{me?}
<C>__{helena}
<D>__{yes, i could smell it on his breath, like i can on your's.}
<A>__{a taut instant between ross and berlin. berlin caught out and he knows it. ross roars in silence "you lying pig" and writes in his notebook. the angle switches to see "berlin is a liar."}
<D>__{i'm late .. i really have to go ..}
<A>__{everyone suddenly on their feet and helena gets into a jacket.}
